Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.13,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胜负仅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:45.23,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 点燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:52.69,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多赐予
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.67,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盗走前 你看 爱在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.93,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感触到了热气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:04.11,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.11,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
